<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI 통합 모니터링 — 전체 아키텍처</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
      background: #0d1117;
      color: #e6edf3;
      padding: 32px;
      min-width: 1200px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f0f6fc;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #7d8590;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .arch {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0;
    }

    /* ── 공통 섹션 ── */
    .section {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1100px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px 24px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1.2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }

    .section-hq     { background: #161b22; border: 1.5px solid #1f4068; }
    .section-bundle { background: #161b22; border: 1.5px dashed #d29922; }
    .section-site   { background: #161b22; border: 1.5px solid #238636; }

    .section-hq     .section-label { color: #58a6ff; }
    .section-bundle .section-label { color: #e3b341; }
    .section-site   .section-label { color: #3fb950; }

    /* ── 연결 화살표 ── */
    .connector {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 4px 0;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .connector-line {
      width: 2px;
      height: 18px;
      background: #444c56;
    }
    .connector-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #7d8590;
      background: #0d1117;
      padding: 2px 12px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    /* ── HQ 내부 ── */
    .hq-inner { display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: flex-start; }

    .git-box {
      flex: 1;
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #1f4068;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
    }
    .git-box h3 {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #58a6ff;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .git-tree {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-family: 'Consolas', monospace;
      color: #8b949e;
      line-height: 1.9;
    }
    .git-tree .hl { color: #e3b341; }

    .hq-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; min-width: 210px; }

    .mini-box {
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
    }
    .mini-box h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .mini-box p  { font-size: 11px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.6; }

    .badge {
      display: inline-block; font-size: 10px;
      padding: 1px 7px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 600;
    }
    .badge-blue   { background: #1f4068; color: #58a6ff; }
    .badge-green  { background: #1a3424; color: #3fb950; }
    .badge-gray   { background: #21262d; color: #8b949e; }
    .badge-orange { background: #2d1f00; color: #e3b341; }

    /* ── Bundle 내부 ── */
    .bundle-inner { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

    .bundle-item {
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #d29922;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      flex: 1; min-width: 160px;
    }
    .bundle-item h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #e3b341; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .bundle-item ul { list-style: none; font-size: 11px; color: #8b949e; line-height: 2; }
    .bundle-item ul li::before { content: '├ '; color: #444c56; }
    .bundle-item ul li:last-child::before { content: '└ '; }

    /* ── Site 내부 ── */
    .site-inner { display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: stretch; }

    .monitoring-server {
      flex: 1.3;
      background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #238636;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 16px;
    }
    .monitoring-server h3 {
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #3fb950;
      margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    }
    .dc-badge {
      font-size: 10px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;
      background: #1a3424; color: #3fb950; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .services-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px; }

    .service-box {
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .service-box:hover { border-color: #58a6ff; }
    .service-name { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
    .service-port { font-size: 11px; color: #7d8590; font-family: monospace; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .service-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.5; }

    .svc-grafana    .service-name { color: #f46800; }
    .svc-prometheus .service-name { color: #e6522c; }
    .svc-loki       .service-name { color: #f0a500; }
    .svc-ollama     .service-name { color: #a78bfa; }
    .svc-fastapi    .service-name { color: #06b6d4; }
    .svc-n8n        .service-name { color: #ea4b71; }

    /* 사이트 내부 화살표 */
    .site-arrow {
      display: flex; flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      gap: 6px; min-width: 56px;
    }
    .arrow-tag {
      font-size: 10px; color: #7d8590; background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d; padding: 2px 6px;
      border-radius: 4px; white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .arrow-line {
      width: 2px; height: 60px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        to bottom, #444c56 0,#444c56 6px, transparent 6px, transparent 12px
      );
    }
    .arrow-head { font-size: 18px; color: #444c56; line-height: 1; }

    /* 수집 대상 서버들 */
    .target-servers {
      flex: 1; background: #0d1117;
      border: 1px solid #30363d; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px;
    }
    .target-servers h3 { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 14px; }

    .server-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 14px; }

    .server-item {
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 14px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 8px;
    }
    .server-name  { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #e6edf3; }
    .server-alloy { font-size: 11px; font-family: monospace; color: #7d8590; }

    .alloy-box {
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #1f4068;
      border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 14px;
    }
    .alloy-box h4 {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #58a6ff;
      margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .collect-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      font-size: 11px; color: #8b949e; margin-bottom: 5px;
    }
    .collect-item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .cicon { width: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; }
    .cmethod {
      margin-left: auto; font-size: 10px; font-family: monospace;
      color: #444c56; background: #0d1117;
      padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 4px;
    }

    /* ── 데이터 흐름 ── */
    .flow-panel {
      width: 100%; max-width: 1100px;
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 24px; margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .panel-title {
      font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #7d8590;
      letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .flow-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 10px; }

    .flow-item {
      background: #0d1117; border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 14px; border-left: 3px solid;
    }
    .flow-item.blue   { border-color: #58a6ff; }
    .flow-item.cyan   { border-color: #06b6d4; }
    .flow-item.green  { border-color: #3fb950; }
    .flow-item.orange { border-color: #e3b341; }
    .flow-item.pink   { border-color: #ea4b71; }
    .flow-item.purple { border-color: #a78bfa; }

    .flow-title { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .flow-item.blue   .flow-title { color: #58a6ff; }
    .flow-item.cyan   .flow-title { color: #06b6d4; }
    .flow-item.green  .flow-title { color: #3fb950; }
    .flow-item.orange .flow-title { color: #e3b341; }
    .flow-item.pink   .flow-title { color: #ea4b71; }
    .flow-item.purple .flow-title { color: #a78bfa; }

    .flow-desc { font-size: 11px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.7; font-family: monospace; }

    /* ── 타임라인 ── */
    .timeline-panel {
      width: 100%; max-width: 1100px;
      background: #161b22; border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 24px; margin-top: 12px;
    }
    .timeline-track { display: flex; }

    .tl-item { flex: 1; padding: 10px 14px; background: #0d1117; border-top: 3px solid; }
    .tl-item:first-child { border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; }
    .tl-item:last-child  { border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; }
    .tl-item.w1 { border-color: #1f4068; }
    .tl-item.w2 { border-color: #238636; }
    .tl-item.w3 { border-color: #a78bfa; }
    .tl-item.w4 { border-color: #e3b341; }

    .tl-weeks { font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; color: #7d8590; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .tl-title { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; color: #e6edf3; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .tl-list  { list-style: none; font-size: 11px; color: #6e7681; line-height: 1.9; }
    .tl-list li::before { content: '· '; }

    footer { text-align: center; font-size: 11px; color: #444c56; margin-top: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>AI Agent 기반 지능형 통합 모니터링 — 전체 아키텍처</h1>
<p class="subtitle">폐쇄망 다환경 배포 &nbsp;·&nbsp; GitOps + 사이트 독립형 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 2인팀 v1</p>

<div class="arch">

  <!-- ══ HQ ══ -->
  <div class="section section-hq">
    <div class="section-label">HQ — 내부망</div>
    <div class="hq-inner">
      <div class="git-box">
        <h3>📁 Git 저장소 (설정 코드 중앙 관리)</h3>
        <div class="git-tree">
          ansible/<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;├── roles/<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── grafana &nbsp;/&nbsp; prometheus &nbsp;/&nbsp; loki<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── ollama &nbsp;/&nbsp; fastapi &nbsp;/&nbsp; n8n<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;└── alloy<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;├── profiles/<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── <span class="hl">bare-metal-highspec.yml</span><br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── <span class="hl">bare-metal-lowspec.yml</span><br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;│&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;└── <span class="hl">docker-only.yml</span><br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;└── sites/<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── <span class="hl">template/</span> &nbsp;← 신규 현장 복사 기준<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;├── site-A / inventory.yml<br>
          &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;└── site-B / inventory.yml
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hq-right">
        <div class="mini-box">
          <h4>⚙️ Ansible Control Node</h4>
          <p>VPN 연결 시 현장에 배포·설정 변경<br>preflight → deploy → rollback</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-box">
          <h4>📡 Health Beacon 집계</h4>
          <p>전체 현장 상태 카드 뷰<br>
            <span class="badge badge-gray">v1: 선택</span>&nbsp;
            <span class="badge badge-green">v2: 표준</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-box">
          <h4>📦 번들 배포 채널</h4>
          <p>USB 드라이브<br>또는 내부 파일 서버 (nginx)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="connector">
    <div class="connector-line"></div>
    <div class="connector-label">오프라인 반입 (USB / 내부 파일서버)</div>
    <div class="connector-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ BUNDLE ══ -->
  <div class="section section-bundle">
    <div class="section-label">오프라인 배포 패키지 &nbsp;·&nbsp; 예상 크기: 20–25 GB</div>
    <div class="bundle-inner">
      <div class="bundle-item">
        <h4>🐳 Docker Images</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>grafana/grafana:10.4.0</li>
          <li>prom/prometheus:v2.51</li>
          <li>grafana/loki:3.0.0</li>
          <li>ollama/ollama:latest</li>
          <li>custom/ai-service (FastAPI)</li>
          <li>n8nio/n8n:latest</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bundle-item">
        <h4>🤖 Ollama 모델 파일</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>llama3.1:8b-instruct (GPU)</li>
          <li>llama3.1:8b-q4_K_M (RAM 16G+)</li>
          <li>phi3.5:3.8b-q4_K_M (RAM 8G+)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bundle-item">
        <h4>📦 RPM / 바이너리</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>grafana-alloy-*.rpm</li>
          <li>docker-ce RPM (미설치 시)</li>
          <li>python3 wheels (FastAPI)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bundle-item">
        <h4>📋 Ansible + 스크립트</h4>
        <ul>
          <li>ansible/ (플레이북 전체)</li>
          <li>install.sh (진입점)</li>
          <li>preflight.yml</li>
          <li>rollback.yml</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="connector">
    <div class="connector-line"></div>
    <div class="connector-label">ansible-playbook deploy.yml &nbsp;(목표: 30분 이내)</div>
    <div class="connector-line"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ SITE ══ -->
  <div class="section section-site">
    <div class="section-label">각 현장 — 폐쇄망 (인터넷 차단 · 업무망 통신 가능)</div>
    <div class="site-inner">

      <!-- 모니터링 서버 -->
      <div class="monitoring-server">
        <h3>🖥️ 모니터링 서버 (1대) <span class="dc-badge">Docker Compose</span></h3>
        <div class="services-grid">
          <div class="service-box svc-grafana">
            <div class="service-name">Grafana</div>
            <div class="service-port">:3000</div>
            <div class="service-desc">대시보드 · 알림<br>실시간 로그 UI</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-box svc-prometheus">
            <div class="service-name">Prometheus</div>
            <div class="service-port">:9090</div>
            <div class="service-desc">메트릭 저장<br>file_sd_configs</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-box svc-loki">
            <div class="service-name">Loki</div>
            <div class="service-port">:3100</div>
            <div class="service-desc">로그 저장<br>LogQL 조회</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-box svc-ollama">
            <div class="service-name">Ollama</div>
            <div class="service-port">:11434</div>
            <div class="service-desc">온프레미스 LLM<br>스펙별 모델 자동 선택</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-box svc-fastapi">
            <div class="service-name">FastAPI</div>
            <div class="service-port">:8000</div>
            <div class="service-desc">AI 분석 API<br>수집 대상 관리 UI</div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-box svc-n8n">
            <div class="service-name">n8n</div>
            <div class="service-port">:5678</div>
            <div class="service-desc">워크플로우 자동화<br>리포트 · 알림 보강</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 화살표 -->
      <div class="site-arrow">
        <div class="arrow-tag">metrics →</div>
        <div class="arrow-tag">logs →</div>
        <div class="arrow-line"></div>
        <div class="arrow-head">◀</div>
        <div class="arrow-tag">scrape</div>
      </div>

      <!-- 수집 대상 서버들 -->
      <div class="target-servers">
        <h3>📡 수집 대상 서버들</h3>
        <div class="server-list">
          <div class="server-item">
            <span class="server-name">서버 A</span>
            <span class="server-alloy">Alloy :12345</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">운영중</span>
          </div>
          <div class="server-item">
            <span class="server-name">서버 B</span>
            <span class="server-alloy">Alloy :12345</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">운영중</span>
          </div>
          <div class="server-item">
            <span class="server-name">서버 C</span>
            <span class="server-alloy">Alloy :12345</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">운영중</span>
          </div>
          <div class="server-item">
            <span class="server-name">서버 D</span>
            <span class="server-alloy">Alloy :12345</span>
            <span class="badge badge-green">운영중</span>
          </div>
          <div class="server-item">
            <span class="server-name">서버 E</span>
            <span class="server-alloy">Alloy :12345</span>
            <span class="badge badge-orange">추가 예정</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alloy-box">
          <h4>ALLOY 수집 항목 (node_exporter 불필요)</h4>
          <div class="collect-item">
            <span class="cicon">💾</span>
            <span>DISK / CPU / RAM</span>
            <span class="cmethod">exporter.unix</span>
          </div>
          <div class="collect-item">
            <span class="cicon">⚙️</span>
            <span>데몬 · 앱 상태</span>
            <span class="cmethod">systemd collector</span>
          </div>
          <div class="collect-item">
            <span class="cicon">🔌</span>
            <span>포트 연결 가능 여부</span>
            <span class="cmethod">exporter.blackbox</span>
          </div>
          <div class="collect-item">
            <span class="cicon">📄</span>
            <span>앱 로그 · 시스템 로그</span>
            <span class="cmethod">loki.source.*</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ 데이터 흐름 ══ -->
  <div class="flow-panel">
    <div class="panel-title">데이터 흐름</div>
    <div class="flow-grid">
      <div class="flow-item blue">
        <div class="flow-title">운영자 → 대시보드</div>
        <div class="flow-desc">Grafana :3000<br>대시보드 조회 / 실시간 로그</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item cyan">
        <div class="flow-title">운영자 → 자연어 질의</div>
        <div class="flow-desc">FastAPI /api/analyze<br>→ Ollama → Prometheus → 요약</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item green">
        <div class="flow-title">운영자 → 수집 대상 관리</div>
        <div class="flow-desc">FastAPI /admin<br>→ targets.json → Prometheus 30초 반영</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item orange">
        <div class="flow-title">n8n → 일일 리포트</div>
        <div class="flow-desc">Cron 08:00<br>→ Prometheus → Ollama → 발송</div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-item pink">
